245
00:41:52,888 --> 00:41:55,057
<i>"Could it have been out of spite?</i>

246
00:41:55,140 --> 00:41:58,101
<i>"My first guess would have been
that the men here were starving.</i>

247
00:41:58,185 --> 00:42:01,230
<i>"But this rotting waste speaks to the contrary.</i>

248
00:42:01,605 --> 00:42:04,107
<i>"The caves are an even bigger mystery.</i>

249
00:42:04,233 --> 00:42:07,027
