250
00:42:07,110 --> 00:42:09,029
<i>"Perhaps they were frightened.</i>

251
00:42:09,112 --> 00:42:11,782
<i>"Maybe there had been some sort of revolt.</i>

252
00:42:12,157 --> 00:42:15,285
<i>"I can make no sense of the clues left me here.</i>

253
00:42:15,494 --> 00:42:18,372
